  "text": "Proteins from total homogenates were resolved in 10% or 15% acrylamide gels for SDS-PAGE and transferred to Immobilon sheets. Membranes were incubated with the following antibodies: anti-DOR (1/200) generated in our laboratory [CITATION_1] , anti-TP53INP1 (1/100, Santa Cruz), anti-p62 (1/1000, BD), anti-LC3 (1/1000, MBL), anti-beta-actin antibody (1/10000, Sigma) or anti-tubulin (1/8000, Sigma). ECL detection was performed as described [CITATION_2] .",
